WEBVTT

00:03.203 --> 00:07.606
Will, I'm ready. You said you'd teach me
one of your basketball tricks.

00:07.974 --> 00:11.375
Oh, well, you know,
my moves are kind of like top secret, Nick.

00:11.544 --> 00:15.412
I mean, I could show you,
but then I'd have to kill you.

00:15.882 --> 00:17.782
Okay.

00:17.951 --> 00:20.715
Well, maybe I'll make an exception
this one time, all right?

00:20.887 --> 00:22.514
All right. Come on. D me up, D me up.

00:25.458 --> 00:26.550
All right, check it out.

00:26.726 --> 00:29.718
Now, this is called the Will Smith
Hoop Dream, Dunk on Hakeem...

00:29.896 --> 00:33.696
...Down the Lane, House of Pain pass.
I see you wasn't ready for that one.

00:33.867 --> 00:36.665
Back in Philly, they used to call me
Will "The 747" Smith.

00:37.303 --> 00:38.327
- Wanna know why?
- Why?

00:43.176 --> 00:45.201
Because I'm about to jet.

